OL,3,CMeet Luke Akehurst: One of the North
OL,4,CEast's most controversial MPs
OL,6,FOne of the most high profile - and
OL,7,Fmost controversial - MPs elected in
OL,8,Fthe North East is North Durham MP Luke
OL,9,FAkehurst.
OL,11,FLabour's National Executive Committee
OL,12,Fselected Mr Akehurst as the
OL,13,Fconstituency candidate, with no vote
OL,14,Ffor local party members, during the
OL,15,F2024 General Election.
OL,17,FHe had been parachuted into the seat
OL,18,Fafter veteran MP Kevan Jones announced
OL,19,Fhe was standing down on health grounds.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
