OL,3,CMeet Luke Akehurst: One of the North
OL,4,CEast's most controversial MPs
OL,6,F"Though I don't have a personal
OL,7,Fconnection there, I felt I would be a
OL,8,Fgood political fit there," Mr Akehurst
OL,9,Fexplained. "Because you look at the
OL,10,Fprevious MPs, Kevan Jones and Giles
OL,11,FRadice, they're both broadly from the
OL,12,Fsame wing of the party as me."
OL,14,FThe 52-year-old, who grew up in the
OL,15,FSouth East, secured 16,562 votes in
OL,16,Fthe election.
OL,18,FMr Akehurst believes that he will be
OL,19,Fable to handle any political battle,
OL,20,Fcalling it as being "comparatively
OL,21,Feasy" following a neurological illness.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
