OL,3,CMeet Luke Akehurst: One of the North
OL,4,CEast's most controversial MPs
OL,6,FMr Akehurst previously worked as a
OL,7,Fformer councillor in the London
OL,8,Fborough of Hackney, and served on
OL,9,FLabour's governing body the National
OL,10,FExecutive Committee.
OL,12,FHe also held roles in the Labour First
OL,13,Fgroup, and Labour To Win.
OL,15,FOne of his most controversial roles,
OL,16,Fis his involvement for the We Believe
OL,17,Fin Israel group, and being a pro-
OL,18,FIsrael lobbyist.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
