OL,3,CMeet Luke Akehurst: One of the North
OL,4,CEast's most controversial MPs
OL,6,FNews of Labour's appointment for its
OL,7,FNorth Durham candidate caused anger by
OL,8,Fpro-Palestine campaigners, who
OL,9,Fprotested against his selection.
OL,11,FIsrael's bombardment and offensives in
OL,12,FGaza have killed more than 38,200
OL,13,Fpeople, and wounded more than 88,000.
OL,15,FMr Akehurst has been a fierce defender
OL,16,Fof Israel's military action in Gaza.
OL,18,FITV Tyne Tees Politics Correspondent
OL,19,FTom Sheldrick asked him, "Is there a
OL,20,Fnumber of civilian deaths in Gaza that
OL,21,Fwould stop you defending Israel?"
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
