OL,3,CMeet Luke Akehurst: One of the North
OL,4,CEast's most controversial MPs
OL,6,FIn response, he said: "The
OL,7,Forganisation that I ran, and my
OL,8,Fpersonal beliefs, and the manifesto of
OL,9,Fthe Labour party are committed to a
OL,10,Ftwo-state solution where, as well as
OL,11,FIsrael being a Jewish state, that
OL,12,Fthere's a free independent state for
OL,13,Fthe Palestinians.
OL,15,F"I agreed with the stance the Labour
OL,16,Fparty had in its manifesto about the
OL,17,Fcurrent war in Gaza, that there needs
OL,18,Fto be a stop to the killing."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
