OL,3,CMeet Luke Akehurst: One of the North
OL,4,CEast's most controversial MPs
OL,6,FWe put Mr Akehurst to the test,
OL,7,Ffinding out how much he knows about
OL,8,Fhis new constituency in a quick fire
OL,9,Fround of questions.
OL,11,FAll three answers were correct.
OL,13,FWhen asked about his priorities for
OL,14,FNorth Durham, and the region as a
OL,15,Fwhole, he said he was focused on
OL,16,F"investment and jobs."
OL,18,F"Even if we're not able to immediately
OL,19,Fincrease the overall package of
OL,20,Fgovernment spending, we can make sure
OL,21,Fit's distributed more fairly."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
